蟤字的基本解释

蟤
zhuān
〔蜿（
w僴 ）蟤〕a.弯曲不伸的样子，如“龙屈蟤蟤。”b.蛇。

蟤字的汉语字典释义

[①]［zhuān］
［《廣韻》莊緣切，平仙，莊。］
见“蜿蟤”。

蟤字的康熙字典解释

【申集中】【虫字部】　蟤； 康熙笔画：18； 页码：页1097第12
【唐韻】【集韻】?莊緣切，音跧。蜿蟤，龍屈貌。【王逸·九思】龍屈兮蜿蟤。【註】蜿蟤，自迫促貌。　又從緣切，音全。蜿蟤，蛇名。　又【類篇】茁撰切。蜿蟤，蟲不申貌。

Kangxi dictionary interpretation of words
[Shenzhen Collection] [Insect Character Department] 　蟤; Kangxi Strokes: 18; Page Number: Page 1097 Page 12
[Tang Yun] [Ji Yun]? Zhuangyuan cuts, and the sound is awkward. Winding, long curving appearance. 【Wang Yi·Jiu Si】The dragon is curving and winding. [Note] Winding, self-compulsive to promote appearance.　 Cut from the edge again, the sound is full. Winding 蟤, the name of the snake.　[Classes] Zhuo essays and cuts. Winding, worms do not show their appearance.
